ectors. Imagine being charged N50 for every deposit you make via Quickteller or internet banking; or being deducted N30 every time you fund your account via the mobile USSD service. Now think about the millions of deposits made into betting accounts per day. That is some serious money we are talking about. Football players including managers and other staffs also experienced salary pay cut during the pandemic period to reduce the burden on the clubs as there were no income coming from ticket sales. In as much as the covid 19 has halted so any activities we will like you to remember that your Health is in your own hands, look after it. Wealth is only meaningful if you can share and also enjoy while you are still alive, kicking & healthy. What you do for yourself, dies with you. But what you do for others will live forever. How to make money from sports betting during the lockdown Have you lost your source of income, or you experienced pay cut due to the Covid 19 pandemics and you thinking of how to generate other streams of income Maybe you are a regular or occasional bettor, you bet for fun or bet to make more profit, Here is what @MC LIVELY also known as BARRISTER MIKE (BM) has to say about Eagle predict as being the most accurate soccer prediction website https://youtu.be/qh0CnDpcqL8. You can click the website link below to access the best free football predictions site, when you think of sure prediction and accurate soccer prediction site that can make you increase your success rate in sports betting, we are the bettors choice for accurate soccer betting tips and there are so many ways to win consistently when you trust the best soccer prediction site in the world for soccer betting tips. If you have any questions, you can contact us on our website and social media handles on Instagram, twitter and facebook For more details on our products and services, please feel free to visit us for SURE 2 ODDS, SURE 3 ODDS, SURE 5 ODDS, DAILY ROLL OVER ODDS & OVER 50 ODDS. FR